{
  "stem": "628.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, in America, they do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But there's nobody who lived it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I said, what are you talking about?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I put up my arm and I showed him my number.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The chief ambassador-- he nearly sank in the floor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[GERMAN] I was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was there in Birkenau and all that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not possible, he said.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think it's time that you do tell the young generation about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyhow, we left the petition there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went back to Ghent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the newspapermen-- it was-- read my story in the book.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the next or two days after he put two pages full, Helmut Szprycer, Birkenau boy, Mengele.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The whole papers were full.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's how the story came out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then people wrote me letters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People telephoned me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "People stopped me on the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That you suffer like this is unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then I started, because the Auschwitz lies, these right extremes, I put them down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I start telling my story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's why I'm here also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's why I came also to-- what's it called?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I hear it on the television, Walesa is not allowing it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Walesa is wants to do it this way, there's more Poles and this there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's no kaddish to be said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, what is wrong there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I hear Weisel comes to say kaddish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said to my wife, I'm going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's for today, for the anniversary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, what do you mean?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not going to-- I'm going to go there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she said, how are you going to go there?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She says, last minute, all hotels are full.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I telephoned.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were all full.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
